cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.NA 

The paper proposes a new approach for image processing, specifically for pattern recognition. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves the evaluation of vector fields, which falls under the category of cs.GR (Graphics). Additionally, the paper involves mathematical calculations and algorithms, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.IT (Information Theory). Finally, the paper involves numerical methods for solving equations, which could fall under cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
